videos.description: Khalil Tate connects with Jamie Nunley, who runs 48 yards untouched for the score to give the Wildcats a lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Tate finds a wide open Nunley for TD

videos.description: Arizona's Shun Brown has the ball bounce off his helmet for a fumble, which is recovered by the Cougars.
videos.headline: Washington State recovers muffed punt

videos.description: Washington State QB Luke Falk finds his WR Isaiah Johnson-Mack for the 1-yard touchdown pass in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Falk connects with Johnson-Mack for TD

videos.description: Shun Brown catches a screen pass from his QB Khalil Tate and takes it 17 yards for the score.
videos.headline: Brown takes screen pass for TD

videos.description: Khalil Tate takes a keeper 82 yards to the Washington State 2-yard line in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Tate sprints down sideline for 82 yards

videos.description: Washington State QB Tyler Hilinski takes it in from 6 yards out after having all day in the pocket.
videos.headline: Hilinski keeps it himself for TD

videos.description: True freshman Josh Pollack blasts a 57 yard field goal as time expires in the first half for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Pollack knocks in 57-yard FG

videos.description: Arizona defensive back Tony Fields II intercepts Washington State's Tyler Hilinski in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Wildcat defense forces turnover

videos.description: The Cougar defense recovers a Khalil Tate fumble seconds after their offense turns it over in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Cougar defense forces fumble
ARIZ VS WSU

videos.description: Arizona QB Khalil Tate is intercepted by Jahad Woods after the ball is tipped up into the air.
videos.headline: Cougar defense gets 2nd turnover of quarter

videos.description: Washington State's Tyler Hilinski gives the Cougars the lead with a 1-yard touchdown run in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Hilinski gets 2nd rushing TD of night

videos.description: Arizona running back J.J. Taylor runs right through the heart of the Cougar defense for a 62-yard gain.
videos.headline: Taylor sprints through the defense for 62 yards

videos.description: J.J. Taylor caps off an impressive drive with a 3-yard touchdown, giving the Wildcats the lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Taylor pounds through for TD

videos.description: Lorenzo Burns intercepts Tyler Hilinski after the ball goes through the hands of a Washington State wide receiver.
videos.headline: Burns picks off Hilinski

videos.description: Arizona defensive back Jace Whittaker picks off Tyler Hilinski in the end zone dashing the Cougars scoring chances.
videos.headline: Whittaker gets interception in end zone

videos.description: Arizona's J.J. Taylor gashes Washington State's defense with a 79-yard touchdown run in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Taylor takes it 79 yards for TD

videos.description: Arizona QB Khalil Tate sprints for a 49-yard touchdown to extend the Wildcats lead in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Tate takes it untouched for TD

videos.description: Arizona's Colin Schooler intercepts Tyler Hilinski and returns it 66 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Wildcats defense gets pick-six

videos.description: Tavares Martin Jr. scores his second touchdown of the night evading multiple defenders on his way to the end zone.
videos.headline: Martin goes 49 yards for TD

videos.description: Wildcats running back Zach Green bullies his way into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Green powers his way for TD
